Package: financialDataAnalysis
Title: A shiny app for scoring, viewing and plotting financial data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ashby", "Thorpe", , "ashbythorpe@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3106-099X"))
Description: Score, view and plot data. The package includes a rich default 
    dataset of stock data, but allows the user to upload their own data. A 
    predictive model is included to forecast the price of a stock over time.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
